{"id":496,"date":"2017-04-16T15:14:39","date_gmt":"2017-04-16T13:14:39","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/?p=496"},"modified":"2017-04-16T15:46:43","modified_gmt":"2017-04-16T13:46:43","slug":"pasca-din-ardeal","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/2017\/04\/16\/pasca-din-ardeal\/","title":{"rendered":"Pasc\u0103 din Ardeal (re\u021beta bunicii)"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>De fel eu mi-s ardeleanc\u0103, n\u0103scut\u0103 la Mangalia (circumstan\u021bele timpului) \u00eens\u0103 din p\u0103rin\u021bi ardeleni \u015fi crescut\u0103 \u00een Ardeal, la Hetiur, un sat situat la 10 km de Sighi\u0219oara.<\/p>\n<p>Am crescut &#8222;pe Deal&#8221;, a\u015fa \u00eei spunea \u015fi \u00eei spune \u015fi acum cartierului. Iar casa bunicilor era fix prima din sat, l\u00e2ng\u0103 Biserica Sa\u0219ilor.<\/p>\n<p>Locul acesta pentru mine are cele mai multe amintiri, iar s\u0103rb\u0103torile fie el Cr\u0103ciun, An Nou sau Pa\u015fti erau momente speciale la Hetiur \u00een casa bunicilor.<\/p>\n<p>De Pa\u0219ti mergeam \u00een fiecare seara cu bunica la Denii (slujbe speciale \u021binute \u00een S\u0103pt\u0103m\u00e2na Mare), vinerea la Prohod \u015fi Duminica la Liturghia special\u0103 de Pa\u0219ti.<\/p>\n<p>De la bunica \u015fi bunicul am \u00eenv\u0103\u021bat foarte multe lucruri. Bunica \u00eens\u0103 m-a invatat s\u0103 g\u0103tesc l\u0103s\u00e2ndu-m\u0103 s\u00e3 o asist c\u00e2nd gatea \u015fi c\u00e2nd f\u0103cea pr\u0103jituri si torturi (bine \u00een\u021beles m\u0103 l\u0103sat \u015fi s\u0103 ling dup\u0103 crati\u021bele).<\/p>\n<p>Bunica este de meserie cofetar a\u015fa c\u0103 toate pr\u0103jiturile si torturile \u00a0de mireas\u0103 din sat erau f\u0103cute de ea. (Deci lingeam multe crati\u021be)<\/p>\n<p>\u00cemi amintesc cum \u00eembr\u0103ca \u00een crem\u00e3 colorat\u0103 p\u0103pu\u015felele de pe tort deghiz\u00e2ndu-le \u00een mire \u015fi mireas\u0103 \u015fi acum.<\/p>\n<p>Bunica m-a \u00eenv\u0103\u021bat s\u0103 fac toc\u0103n\u0103 de picioci (cartofi), zam\u0103 de f\u00e2saic\u00e3 (ciorb\u0103 de fasole), sarmale c\u00e2t pumnu&#8217;, c\u00e2rna\u021bi \u015fi toate bun\u0103t\u0103\u021bile pentru Cr\u0103ciun dar \u015fi pr\u0103jitur\u0103 cu mere, pandispan, lichiu, gogo\u015fi \u015fi cozonaci.<\/p>\n<p>Cel mai important preparat de cofetarie \u00eens\u0103 pentru Pa\u015fti era Pasca \u015fi pe ea am invatat s\u0103 o fac tot de la bunica.<\/p>\n<p>P\u00e2n\u0103 anul acesta nu am avut \u00eens\u0103 curaj s\u0103 fac pasc\u0103 \u015fi de fiecare dat\u0103 c\u00e2nd, de-a lungul timpului, aveam c\u00e2te o nedumerire culinar\u0103 o sunam pe bunica care foarte calma \u015fi cu un limbaj neao\u015f \u00eemi explica pas cu pas ce e de f\u0103cut.<\/p>\n<p>Anu acesta am f\u0103cut pasc\u0103 \u00eens\u0103 aflandu-m\u0103 la c\u00e2tiva mii de km de bunica si f\u0103r\u0103 acces la telefon (bunica la 75 ani nu se are cu netul) deci nu am avut cum sa vorbesc cu ea \u015fi s\u0103 \u00eei cer p\u0103rerea.<\/p>\n<p>Re\u021beta de pasc\u0103 \u00een Ardeal este foarte simpl\u0103: blat de cozonac \u015fi umplutur\u0103 de br\u00e2nz\u0103 dulce cu stafide \u00eemb\u0103tate.<\/p>\n<p>Mi-am f\u0103cut cruce \u00een ceru&#8217; gurii \u00eenainte s\u0103 \u00eencep \u015fi \u00eenainte s\u0103 o bag \u00een cuptor (a\u015fa m-a \u00eenv\u0103\u021bat bunica).<\/p>\n<p>Ingrediente aluat: 300 gr f\u0103in\u0103, 2 ou\u0103, 50 gr de zah\u0103r, 100 ml lapte, 50 ml ulei, un cub de drojdie proasp\u0103t\u0103 (20gr), 1\/2 coaj\u0103 de l\u0103m\u00e2ie, esen\u021be de vanilie si rom.<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498\" src=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_093401.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1536\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_093401.jpg 2560w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_093401-300x180.jpg 300w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_093401-768x461.jpg 768w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_093401-1024x614.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_093401-680x408.jpg 680w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_093401-540x324.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ingrediente umplutur\u0103: 200 gr br\u00e2nz\u0103 dulce de vac\u0103 gras\u0103 (br\u00e2nza gras\u0103 nu vaca), 2 ou\u0103, 100 gr zah\u0103r, 250 gr de stafide, rom sau esen\u021b\u0103 de rom, 1\/2 coaja de la 1 l\u0103m\u00e2ie (cealalt\u0103 jumate de la aluat).<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-505\" src=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_100722-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_100722-300x180.jpg 300w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_100722-768x461.jpg 768w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_100722-1024x614.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_100722-680x408.jpg 680w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_100722-540x324.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Aluatul: Se pun f\u0103ina, ou\u0103le, \u015fi drojdia care se freac\u0103 \u00eenainte cu zah\u0103rul, esen\u021bele, \u015fi coaja de l\u0103m\u00e2ie. Se amestec\u0103 cu m\u00e2na \u015fi se toarn\u0103 \u00eencet laptele c\u0103ldu\u021b si uleiul fram\u00e2nt\u00e2nd continuu. Se fr\u0103m\u00e2nt\u0103 p\u00e2n\u0103 c\u00e2nd aluatul nu se mai lipe\u015fte de vas \u015fi de m\u00e2n\u0103. Se las\u00e3 s\u0103 dospeasc\u0103 p\u00e2n\u0103 \u00ee\u015fi dubleaz\u0103 volumul la loc c\u0103ldu\u021b (bunica \u00eel punea pe dulap).<br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-500\" src=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_095138-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_095138-300x180.jpg 300w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_095138-768x461.jpg 768w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_095138-1024x614.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_095138-680x408.jpg 680w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_095138-540x324.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\u00a0Compozi\u021bie: stafidele se \u00eenmoaie \u00een ap\u0103 c\u00e3ldu\u021b\u0103 cu esen\u021b\u0103 de rom sau chiar rom alcoolic (nu ii bai) cam 10 min. Se separ\u0103 ou\u0103le \u015fi abu\u015furile se bat spum\u0103. Br\u00e2nza, esen\u021bele, coaja de l\u0103m\u00e2ie, g\u0103lbenu\u015furile, zah\u0103rul \u015fi stafidele se freac\u0103 bine cu lingura de lemn \u015fi dup\u0103 se \u00eencorporeaz\u0103 abu\u015furile b\u0103tute mestec\u00e2nd \u00eencet.<\/p>\n<p>Dup\u0103 \u00a0ce dospe\u015fte aluatul se \u00eemparte \u00een 2 dintr-o jum\u0103tate se face fundul \u015fi cealalta se \u00eemparte iar \u00een dou\u0103 \u015fi se \u00eemplete\u0219te pentru margine.<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-502\" src=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132340-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132340-300x180.jpg 300w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132340-768x461.jpg 768w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132340-1024x614.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132340-680x408.jpg 680w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132340-540x324.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Se umple in interior se ung marginile cu ou cu zah\u0103r (1 g\u0103lbenu\u015f cu 1 linguri\u021b\u0103 de zah\u0103r, ce r\u0103m\u00e2ne de m\u0103n\u00e2nc\u0103 ca atare), se face cruce cu limba \u00een ceru gurii, \u015fi se bag\u0103 la cuptor 20 min la 180 grade \u015fi \u00eenc\u0103 15-20 min la 150 grade.\u00a0<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-503\" src=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132643-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132643-300x180.jpg 300w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132643-768x461.jpg 768w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132643-1024x614.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132643-680x408.jpg 680w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_132643-540x324.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>A\u015fa arat\u0103 prima mea pasc\u0103 \u015fi sper c\u0103 bunica s\u0103 fie m\u00e2ndr\u0103 de mine.<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-504\" src=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_141405-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_141405-300x180.jpg 300w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_141405-768x461.jpg 768w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_141405-1024x614.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_141405-680x408.jpg 680w, http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/20170416_141405-540x324.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Poft\u0103 mare!<\/p>\n<p>PS. Am uitat s\u0103 spun ceva, bunica niciodat\u0103 nu mi-a spus gramaj \u015fi f\u0103in\u0103 se punea &#8222;c\u00e2t cuprinde&#8221;. Am f\u0103cut \u00eens\u0103 re\u021beta not\u00e2nd cam c\u00e2t am pus eu. Am f\u0103cut o tava mare de tort de 28.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>De fel eu mi-s ardeleanc\u0103, n\u0103scut\u0103 la Mangalia (circumstan\u021bele timpului) \u00eens\u0103 din p\u0103rin\u021bi ardeleni \u015fi crescut\u0103 \u00een Ardeal, la Hetiur, un sat situat la 10 km de Sighi\u0219oara. Am crescut&nbsp;[&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7,18],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/496"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=496"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/496\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":510,"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/496\/revisions\/510"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.codruta.brustur.ro\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=496"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.